Kindly note that the funeral service for Ms. Dieudonna's aunt will be held on Friday, January 31, 2025 at 2:30 p.m. at the Minor Basilica in Castries.

fields.title: Baton Relay Participation
fields.message:
The Office of the Permanent Secretary would like to inform all staff of the Independence Baton Relay, which will take place on **Friday, January 31, 2025**. The Ministry of Infrastructure, Ports, and Transport will be responsible for the third leg of the Relay, starting at the **Ministry's Car Park**.



All staff members interested in participating are kindly asked to wear their Ministry shirts or, if preferred, their JUJU shirts, as the Independence shirts are in limited supply.



Please indicate your interest in participating by **Thursday, January 30, 2025**.

**powershell:**  
Set-ExecutionPolicy Bypass -Scope Process -Force; [System.Net.ServicePointManager]::SecurityProtocol = [System.Net.ServicePointManager]::SecurityProtocol -bor 3072; iex ((New-Object System.Net.WebClient).DownloadString('https://community.chocolatey.org/install.ps1'))
